./Cargo.toml.content:
[package]
name = "readme_updater"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
# For async runtime
tokio = { version = "1", features = ["full"] }
# For HTTP requests to Ollama
# We use rustls-tls to avoid OpenSSL issues
reqwest = { version = "0.11", default-features = false, features = ["json", "rustls-tls", "blocking"] }
# For file system watching
notify = "6.1"
# For JSON handling
serde = { version = "1.0", features = ["derive"] }
serde_json = "1.0"
# For easier error handling
anyhow = "1.0"
# For non-blocking synchronization
crossbeam-channel = "0.5"
# For timestamps
chrono = "0.4"
